## Configuration and installation details

### Environment variables

For a full overview of the available environment variables and their meaning, 
see the the Open Product [documentation](https://open-product.readthedocs.io/en/stable/installation/config/env_config.html).

### Automatic configuration

The application can be automatically configured with `django-setup-configuration`.
To enable the automatic configuration, the following values should be set:

```yaml
global:
  configuration:
    enabled: true

configuration:
  enabled: true
  job:
    enabled: true
```

The yaml data needed to configure the application should be provided in the value `configuration.data`. To see
how to configure, see the Open Product [documentation](https://open-product.readthedocs.io/en/stable/installation/config/openproduct_config_cli.html).

